OL,7,FMeanwhile, both trusts say they are
OL,8,Fmoving staff up where appropriate.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, Clare
OL,11,FWilliams, from Unison, said: "I think
OL,12,Fit's a real shame that healthcare
OL,13,Fassistants have been forced into
OL,14,Ftaking further strike action because
OL,15,Fthe trust is just refusing to
OL,16,Fnegotiate with unison.
