OL,7,F"They are re-banding so staff get paid
OL,8,Ffor the work they are doing, clinical
OL,9,Fwork on a daily basis, but they also
OL,10,Fneed to negotiate with Unison an
OL,11,Fappropriate deal on backpay.
OL,13,F"Many of these healthcare assistants
OL,14,Fhave worked for years above their pay
OL,15,Fband."
