OL,3,C'They have worked for years above
OL,4,Ctheir pay band' - NHS workers stage
OL,5,Cwalk out
OL,7,FMs Williams continued: "It's really
OL,8,Ftough, we are in a cost of living
OL,9,Fcrisis. Healthcare assistants are some
OL,10,Fof the lowest paid staff. Indeed, many
OL,11,Fof them are earning a penny above the
OL,12,Fnational minimum wage.
OL,14,F"It's not unreasonable for them to say
OL,15,F'pay us at the proper rate for the
OL,16,Fwork we are doing'. It's clinical
OL,17,Fwork, looking after all of us and our
OL,18,Floved ones.
