OL,3,C'They have worked for years above
OL,4,Ctheir pay band' - NHS workers stage
OL,5,Cwalk out
OL,7,F"The trusts need to negotiate an
OL,8,Fappropriate length of back pay, that
OL,9,Frecognises all of the years people
OL,10,Fhave been working under their adequate
OL,11,Fpay band."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for North Tees and
OL,14,FHartlepool NHS Foundation Trust and
OL,15,FSouth Tees Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,16,FTrust said: "We recognise and
OL,17,Fappreciate the huge contribution that
OL,18,Fhealthcare assistants make to our
OL,19,Fpatients.
