OL,3,C'They have worked for years above
OL,4,Ctheir pay band' - NHS workers stage
OL,5,Cwalk out
OL,7,F"Since the elements of these roles
OL,8,Fwere clarified nationally, we have
OL,9,Fbeen working closely with trade union
OL,10,Fcolleagues to move our healthcare
OL,11,Fassistants to these grades where
OL,12,Fapplicable.
OL,14,F"Our trusts support this move and the
OL,15,Fbenefits to our HCA workforce and
OL,16,Ftherefore have committed to back pay
OL,17,Fdating back to July 2021 - the date
OL,18,Fthe national job profile for the
OL,19,Fclinical support worker role changed.
