OL,7,F"During the strike action, we will
OL,8,Fonce again be prioritising urgent and
OL,9,Femergency care to protect patient
OL,10,Fsafety and ensure those in life-
OL,11,Fthreatening emergencies can receive
OL,12,Fthe best possible care."
OL,14,FThe trusts are reminding all patients
OL,15,Fto attend appointments unless they
OL,16,Fhave been rescheduled.
